summary: This mod adds an oven for the dragonborn home. A request from MuaKell, he wanted to bake ashhsopper cakes and make cookies out of netches jelly.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds an oven for the dragonborn home. A request from MuaKell, he wanted to bake ashhsopper cakes and make cookies out of netches jelly.
There is a non respawn bag next to it for the sack of convince.
